data.description: SELLER SUPER MOTIVATED. MAJOR REDUCED PRICE!! New HVAC and Gas Hot Water Heater just installed! Roof 2019. Motivated Seller! Bring Offers! Don't miss this inviting 3 bedroom 2 bath single-story home featuring a split floor plan for ultimate comfort. Step inside to fresh paint , updates throughout, and new carpeting, along with high ceilings and a cozy gas fireplace in the living room. You'll love the sun-filled Florida Room, a screened porch for relaxed outdoor living, and a spacious backyard for your enjoyment.
